data.description: NO HOA! New Roof 2022. Over one acre, Stepless Ranch, 3BR/2BA with bonus room. Full daylight basement stubbed for bath and high ceilings just waiting for your finishing touches!  Bonus room above garage has its own A/C system in place, perfect for playroom, additional BR, media room or office. Newer roof and beautifully maintained. Open floor plan is light and bright, family room with fireplace, kitchen with natural stained cabinets and large breakfast room.  Wonderful laundry and mud room with extra pantry space. Oversized owners suite and huge walk in closet. Deck off the breakfast room overlooks your private back yard with room for a pool!  FABULOUS LOCATION!!!!  Just minutes to Publix Grocery Store, Home Depot, Kohls, Chic-fi-la, restaurants, Shopping,  and I-985.  Close to Lake Lanier and the new NE GA Hospital. This is a lovely neighborhood and homes are on larger lots - truly a rare find.
